### Could not extract iron-plate at (0.0, 0.0)
- The agent attempted to extract iron-plate from (0.0, 0.0), but no entity containing iron-plate was found at that location. Ensure that a valid entity containing iron-plate exists at the specified coordinates before attempting to extract.
